{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/2021/10/4/dark-noise-2_6-iOS-15/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"iOS 15 Support with Dark Noise 2.6","date":"04 October, 2021","image":"http://media.charliemchapman.com/blog/dark-noise-mac-rounded_1024.png"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2021/10/4/dark-noise-2_6-iOS-15/"},"html":"<p>Dark Noise 2.6 comes to the <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dark-noise/id1465439395\">App Store today</a> with full support for iOS 15!</p>\n<h2>Extra Large Widgets</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 750px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/6e14f/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.54752851711027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Extra Large Widgets\"\n        title=\"New Extra Large Widgets\"\n        src=\"/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/2a7f3/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/1a190/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 188w,\n/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/992ed/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 375w,\n/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/2a7f3/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 750w,\n/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/f4978/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 1125w,\n/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/db64a/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 1500w,\n/static/0109f1796b151310993abfc1effdb65c/6e14f/dark-noise-2_6-extra-large-widgets.jpg 2630w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>iOS 15 introducted a new widget size exclusive to iPad and Dark Noise 2.6 adds support for these new big sizes. Now you can fill your iPad with 16 wide button noises, or a whopping 32 square button noises in a single widget!</p>\n<p>And of course these widgets support all of the themes and customizations you've come to expect from Dark Noise widgets.</p>\n<h2>Shortcuts</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 750px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/efa1c/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.89617486338798%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Shortcuts Actions\"\n        title=\"New Shortcuts Actions\"\n        src=\"/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/2a7f3/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/1a190/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 188w,\n/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/992ed/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 375w,\n/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/2a7f3/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 750w,\n/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/f4978/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 1125w,\n/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/db64a/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 1500w,\n/static/65688b988418f119055ce1029d3d5675/efa1c/dark-noise-2_6-shortcuts.jpg 3660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Due to limitations in iOS 14, Shortcuts actions with parameters could not play audio without opening the app up in the foreground. This led to a confusing array of Shortcuts actions provided by Dark Noise. Shortcuts with parameters for setting up a timer or volume (began with the word \"Start\") had to open the app to start a sound. And shortcuts with no parameter options (began with the word \"Play\") were limited but could play sounds in the background.</p>\n<p>With iOS 15 things are dramatically simpler. New \"Play [Noise]\" Shortcuts actions can play noises in the background <strong>and</strong> have parameter options for customizations.</p>\n<p>There is also a new Shortcut action called \"Find [Noise]\" for advanced Shortcuts users. This action accepts a string parameter, searches Dark Noise for a matching noise, and outputs a Noise object that the new \"Play [Noise]\" action will accept as an input.</p>\n<p>This allows for more advanced automations where you want to dynamically pass in a string for which noise you would like to play.  To be honest I'm not entirely sure what the main use case for this is, but I've recieved enough requests for it that I thought it was worth adding. I'd love to hear from anybody who uses it to see what they've built!</p>\n<h2>Bug Fixes and Improvements</h2>\n<p>A new timer view using iOS 15's new half sheet popover and some minor bug fixes round out the update. This year's iOS beta cycle has been... busy to say the least (I moved into new house!). Things are finally settling down and I'm getting back to work on Dark Noises next major feature!</p>","excerpt":"Dark Noise 2.6 comes to the App Store today with full support for iOS 15! Extra Large Widgets  iOS 15 introducted a new widget sizeâ€¦"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/2021/10/4/dark-noise-2_6-iOS-15/"}}}